
README

Summary

Simple web page design using Bootstrap for modern looking "responsive" web page.
Mocha/Chai used for TDD/BDD.
Javascript used for interactivity programming.


Prerequisites :-

JavaScript installed
Browser


Instructions for use :-

1. Navigate to sub folder "DarrenB->src".

2. To run the sample web page design, open "productSelection.html" web page in a browser of your choice (Chrome used for design work).
Use as normal web page to select/deselect products in the basket. Click on "Checkout" button to confirm selections and be taken to a confirmation page ("confirmation.html"). 

3. To run the Unit tests with Mocha/Chai Behaviour Driven Development, open the "testProductSelection.html" web page.

